zenpad (1.2.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New Feature: Analysis Tools (Hex, Hash, Encoders/Decoders)
  * New Feature: Markdown Preview (WebKit2)
  * New Feature: Diff Tool (Compare Tabs)
  * Fix: Application freeze on repetitive Convert Log to JSON
  * Fix: Syntax highlighting for certain file types
  * Build: Added dependencies for webkit2 and markdown

