zenpad (1.1.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Release 1.1.0: Huge CLI Update
  * Fix KeyboardInterrupt traceback (#4)
  * Add --version, --quit flags (#5, #6)
  * Add --help flag (#7)
  * Add --preferences flag (#8)
  * Add --line / --column jump support (#9, #10)
  * Add --opening-mode (tab/window/mixed) (#11)
  * Add --encoding flag (#12)
  * Add --list-encodings flag (#13)
  * Add --disable-server flag (#14)
  * Update README source installation instructions (#17)
  * Fix unsaved warning indicator (via PR #18 logic)
  * Fix GtkSource version crash (fallback to 3.0)

